rComments: Parle trop vite. Parle pas assez fort, même quand on lui mentionne qu'il ne parle pas assez fort. Parle beaucoup pour pas dire grand chose. Assez clair en ce qui concerne la matière importante à l'examen. Si tu lis tes textes et que tu écoutes en classe, l'examen ne sera pas si difficile que ça. I wouldn't choose this teacher again..
Best teacher i had yet in civil law

literally the worst class i've taken. Powerpoints consist of paragraphs copy and pasted on slides in various fonts and colours. Prof talks in anecdotes and doesnt explain concepts clearly. You need to know what hes talking about before going to class in order to understand what he's even saying. Avoid if you can, midterm was 14 pages and took 2hrs.
